{"id":"dc970432-050e-46ea-bded-4bf78d409ac4","name":"Rayne | Down On Her Luck","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ddfff5\"><em>\"Don't look at me like some poor stray.\"</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ddfff5\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(230, 200, 142, 0); color: inherit\">━━━━━━━━༻❁༺━━━━━━━━</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ddfff5\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(230, 200, 142, 0); color: inherit\">You were coming home from a late day at work, when the sound of labored breathing just barely reached your ears over the rain. Upon closer inspection, it appeared to be coming from a shaded alleyway. In it, was a bloodied woman looking as if she would kill over within the minute.</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 255, 245)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(230, 200, 142, 0); color: inherit\">━━━━━━━━༻❁༺━━━━━━━━</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 255, 245)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(230, 200, 142, 0); color: inherit\">On The Verge Of Death {{char}}</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 255, 245)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(230, 200, 142, 0); color: inherit\">x</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 255, 245)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(230, 200, 142, 0); color: inherit\">{{user}} That Saved Her</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 255, 245)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(230, 200, 142, 0); color: inherit\">━━━━━━━━༻❁༺━━━━━━━━</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 255, 245)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(230, 200, 142, 0); color: inherit\">Sorry guys... This isn't Ricardo, I know you are all disappointed..... Anyways I saw that they were gonna add pictures to bot descriptions back soon. Awesome. I also am not sure if this counts as dead dove or not.</mark></span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"svyzf0Ie_iE0UWpqQdWIW.webp","creator":"Idal","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","👤 AnyPOV","🕊🗡 Dead Dove"],"chats":2067,"messages":37611,"created_at":"2025-03-24T05:44:32.535576+00:00"}